nodes.text: The Caves of Eleuabad were a system of submerged underground catacombs near the city of Theed on Naboo. It was known as an area where sando aqua monster encounters were common. During the Invasion of Naboo, Qui-Gon Jinn and Obi-Wan Kenobi utilized a Gungan bongo submarine to reach the city of Theed, venturing through the Caves of Eleuabad.
